beer.beer_description: Brewed as part of Bankstown Sports’ greater contribution to the bushfire relief effort, Basement Brewhouse has especially crafted ‘South Coast Ale’. $2 from every ale sold in venue will go directly to those in the South Coast region who have been affected by the recent bushfires. Our South Coast Pale Ale is packed with juicy tropical Australian hops lending aromas of bright Passionfruit and Citrus, making it super refreshing and easy drinking after a long hot day.
